  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To compare the safety and efficacy of the CVI silicone-hydrogel lens worn on an extended wear
      basis for a period of up to 7 days and 6 nights with the Acuvue 2 soft contact lenses.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
